headline: Equifax (EFX) Margin Expansion Surpasses Expectations, Reinforces Bullish Narrative
summary: Equifax (EFX) posted healthy earnings progress in its latest report, with profit margins climbing to 11.1% from 10.1% and annual earnings growth reversing course to hit 17.1% after a tough stretch of five years marked by a 1.2% drop per year. Analysts now expect earnings to grow 20.3% per year over the next three years, well ahead of the broader US market’s 15.5% pace. However, revenue growth is forecast at 8.5% per year, slower than the market’s 10.1% rate. Overall, the combination of higher...
